      "contents": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Strengths\n",
          "bold": true,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Versatile kit allows the astronaut to slot into any team.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Augments can be very powerful and cateams can be built around them.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Variety of projectile abilities can disrupt enemies and minions alike.\n\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Weaknesses\n",
          "bold": true,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Low base gravity can make it difficult to engage against high knockback or projectiles.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Generalist nature might not be ideal depending on the team composition.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Poor melee combat capabilities.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        }
